---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '');
---

<section class="movement-section section-padding" id="the-movement">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="movement-grid">
      <div class="movement-text">
        <span class="section-label animate-in" data-i18n="machine.movement_label">The Movement</span>
        <h2 class="section-title animate-in" data-i18n="machine.movement_headline">What Makes Byron Different</h2>

        <p class="movement-paragraph animate-in" data-i18n="machine.movement_intro">
          Byron Sigcho-Lopez is an ideologically committed democratic socialist and a firebrand who has spent his entire career fighting for the multiracial working class. He is not a politician looking for a promotion. He is an organizer who was called to serve by his community.
        </p>

        <!-- Insurgent Block -->
        <div class="movement-block animate-in">
          <h3 class="movement-block-title" data-i18n="machine.unbought_title">
            <span class="movement-block-icon">🚫</span>
            The Unbought Insurgent
          </h3>
          <p class="movement-block-text" data-i18n="machine.unbought_text">
            Unlike establishment politicians, Byron completely rejects corporate PAC money and contributions from real estate developers. His campaign is powered entirely by thousands of small-dollar grassroots donations from teachers, nurses, union members, and working families. He has upheld this commitment since his first campaign in 2015 and has never wavered.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Tested Record Block -->
        <div class="movement-block animate-in">
          <h3 class="movement-block-title" data-i18n="machine.tested_title">
            <span class="movement-block-icon">✊</span>
            A Tested Record
          </h3>
          <p class="movement-block-text" data-i18n="machine.tested_text">
            Byron's unique power comes from bottom-up organizing. As 25th Ward Alderperson, he passed anti-displacement legislation to protect homeowners from predatory developers, created over 800 units of affordable housing, stood uncompromisingly with the Chicago Teachers Union, doubled the Affordable Requirements Ordinance minimum, and joined a hunger strike to fight environmental racism. These are not campaign promises. These are receipts.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="movement-image-stack animate-in">
        <div class="movement-image-wrap">
          <img
            src={`${base}/images/movement-frontlines.png`}
            alt="Byron organizing with community members in Pilsen"
            class="movement-image"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="movement-pullquote">
          <blockquote data-i18n="machine.pullquote">
            "I have never taken a dollar from a corporation or a developer. I never will. My loyalty is to the people of this district, not to the machine."
          </blockquote>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .movement-section {
    background: var(--cream);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .movement-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
    gap: var(--space-4xl);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .movement-paragraph {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--gray-700);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .movement-block {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--orange);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    transition: transform var(--duration-normal) var(--ease-default), box-shadow var(--duration-normal) var(--ease-default);
  }

  .movement-block:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }

  .movement-block-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--blue);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .movement-block-icon {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
  }

  .movement-block-text {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--gray-700);
  }

  /* Image Stack */
  .movement-image-stack {
    position: sticky;
    top: calc(var(--nav-height) + var(--space-xl));
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .movement-image-wrap {
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }

  .movement-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 400px;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  .movement-pullquote {
    background: var(--blue);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    position: relative;
  }

  .movement-pullquote::before {
    content: '"';
    position: absolute;
    top: -10px;
    left: 16px;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 5rem;
    line-height: 1;
    color: rgba(251, 226, 186, 0.15);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .movement-pullquote blockquote {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--cream);
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .movement-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-2xl);
    }

    .movement-image-stack {
      position: static;
    }

    .movement-image {
      height: 280px;
    }
  }
</style>
